fice;","strongs_def":"Zebach, a Midianitish prince","kjv_def":"Zebah.","pos":"proper masculine noun","usage":"Zebah(12x)"},"H2079":{"id":"H2079","lemma":"זַבַּי","translit":"Zabbay","pron":"zab-bah'-ee","derivation":"probably by orthographical error for H2140 (זַכַּי);","strongs_def":"Zabbai (or Zaccai), an Israelite","kjv_def":"Zabbai.","pos":"proper masculine noun","usage":"Zabbai(2x)"},"H2080":{"id":"H2080","lemma":"זְבִידָה","translit":"Zᵉbîydâh","pron":"zeb-ee-daw'","derivation":"feminine from H2064 (זָבַד); giving;","strongs_def":"Zebidah, an Israelitess","kjv_def":"Zebudah."},"H2081":{"id":"H2081","lemma":"זְבִינָא","translit":"Zᵉbîynâʼ","pron":"zeb-ee-naw'","derivation":"from an unused root (meaning to purchase); gainfulness;","strongs_def":"Zebina, an Israelite","kjv_def":"Zebina.","pos":"proper masculine noun","usage":"Zebina(1x)"},"H2082":{"id":"H2082","lemma":"זָבַל","translit":"zâbal","pron":"zaw-bal'","derivation":"a primitive root; apparently properly, to inclose, i.e.","strongs_def":"to reside","kjv_def":"dwell with.","pos":"verb"},"H2083":{"id":"H2083","lemma":"זְבֻל","translit":"Zᵉbul","pron":"zeb-ool'","derivation":"the same as H2073 (זְבוּל); dwelling;","strongs_def":"Zebul, an Israelite","kjv_def":"Zebul. Compare H2073 (זְבוּל).","pos":"proper masculine noun","usage":"Zebul(6x)"},"H2084":{"id":"H2084","lemma":"זְבַן","translit":"zᵉban","pron":"zeb-an'","derivation":"(Aramaic) corresponding to the root of H2081 (זְבִינָא);","strongs_def":"to acquire by purchase","kjv_def":"gain.","pos":"verb","usage":"gain(1x)"},"H2085":{"id":"H2085","lemma":"זָג","translit":"zâg","pron":"zawg","derivation":"from an unused root probably meaning to inclose;","strongs_def":"the skin of a grape","kjv_def":"husk."},"H2086":{"id":"H2086","lemma":"זֵד","translit":"zêd","pron":"zade'","derivation":"from H2102 (זוּד);","strongs_def":"arrogant","kjv_def":"presumptuous, proud.","pos":"masculine noun","usage":"proud(12x), presumptuous(1x)"},"H2087":{"id":"H2087","lemma":"זָ